### Update category
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/partners/categories/21
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "parent-id": 25
}

### Update - name only
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/partners/categories/21
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Global Manufacturers Update Name Only"
}

### Update - deactivate
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/partners/categories/21
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "active": false
}

### Update - reactivate
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/partners/categories/40
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "active": true
}

### Update - display order only
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/partners/categories/22
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "display-order": 10
}

### Update - all fields including parent
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/partners/categories/31
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Consumer Electronics Manufacturers",
  "active": true,
  "display-order": 1,
  "parent-id": 22
}

### Update - validation error: blank name
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/partners/categories/21
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": ""
}

### Update - validation error: name too long
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/partners/categories/21
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "This partner category name is way too long and exceeds the maximum allowed length of one hundred characters limit"
}

### Update - not found (EntityNotFoundException)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/partners/categories/999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Does Not Exist",
  "active": true,
  "display-order": 1
}